sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User Browser
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant OAuth as OAuth Proxy Sidecar<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Jupyter as Jupyter Container<br/>8888/TCP HTTP
    participant S3 as Object Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant KFP as Kubeflow Pipelines<br/>Controller
    participant Runtime as Runtime Container<br/>Pod
    participant KFPAPI as Kubeflow API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+

    rect rgb(220, 240, 255)
        Note over User,S3: Flow 1: User Accesses Jupyter Workbench
        User->>Router: HTTPS GET /notebook/{namespace}/{username}/lab<br/>TLS 1.2+, No Auth
        Router->>OAuth: Forward request<br/>HTTPS/8443, Internal CA Cert
        OAuth->>OAuth: Validate OpenShift OAuth Token
        OAuth->>Jupyter: HTTP GET /lab<br/>Port 8888, No encryption (localhost)
        Jupyter-->>OAuth: JupyterLab UI Response
        OAuth-->>Router: HTTPS Response
        Router-->>User: HTTPS Response, TLS 1.2+

        Note over Jupyter,S3: User executes notebook code
        Jupyter->>S3: HTTPS GET /bucket/data.csv<br/>Port 443, TLS 1.2+, S3 Credentials
        S3-->>Jupyter: Data file
    end

    rect rgb(255, 240, 220)
        Note over KFP,KFPAPI: Flow 2: Kubeflow Pipeline Task Execution
        KFP->>Runtime: Create Pod<br/>ServiceAccount Token
        Runtime->>S3: HTTPS GET /bucket/model.pkl<br/>Port 443, TLS 1.2+, AWS SigV4
        S3-->>Runtime: Model artifact

        Runtime->>Runtime: Execute ML task<br/>(training/inference)

        Runtime->>S3: HTTPS PUT /bucket/output.pkl<br/>Port 443, TLS 1.2+, AWS SigV4
        S3-->>Runtime: Acknowledgement

        Runtime->>KFPAPI: POST /api/v1/artifacts<br/>Port 443, HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount Token
        KFPAPI-->>Runtime: Success

        Runtime-->>KFP: Task Completed
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over Router,Jupyter: Flow 3: Image Build and Deployment
        participant GitHub as GitHub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
        participant Konflux as Konflux Pipeline<br/>Tekton
        participant UBIReg as UBI Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
        participant QuayIO as Quay.io<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
        participant ImgStream as ImageStream
        participant Kubelet as Kubelet

        Konflux->>GitHub: HTTPS GET /repo/notebooks<br/>Port 443, TLS 1.2+, Git Token
        GitHub-->>Konflux: Source code

        Konflux->>UBIReg: HTTPS Pull base image<br/>Port 443, TLS 1.2+, Pull Secret
        UBIReg-->>Konflux: UBI9 Python image

        Konflux->>Konflux: Build multi-arch image<br/>linux/x86_64, arm64, ppc64le, s390x

        Konflux->>QuayIO: HTTPS Push image<br/>Port 443, TLS 1.2+, Push Secret
        QuayIO-->>Konflux: Image stored

        ImgStream->>QuayIO: HTTPS Pull image reference<br/>Port 443, TLS 1.2+, Pull Secret
        QuayIO-->>ImgStream: Image metadata

        Kubelet->>ImgStream: Resolve image tag
        ImgStream-->>Kubelet: Image URL

        Kubelet->>QuayIO: HTTPS Pull image<br/>Port 443, TLS 1.2+, Pull Secret
        QuayIO-->>Kubelet: Container image layers

        Kubelet->>Kubelet: Start workbench container
    end
